Description:
Immaculate Family Expanse on 733m2
In a blissfully quiet cul-de-sac & spread out on a whopping 733m2, this two-storey home presents an exceptional indoor/outdoor family lifestyle opportunity with its versatile design, 6 car accommodation, quality inclusions & immaculate presentation throughout.
Surrounded by established gardens, the home's pristine interior comprises 5 main bedrooms, 1 conveniently placed downstairs (large master upstairs with his/hers robes & private ensuite), updated stylish family bathrooms & guest powder room (3rd WC). Multiple living zones include an elegant formal lounge & adjoining dining area, large rumpus (upstairs) with leafy outlook & open-plan family/meals area accompanied by a well-appointed stone top kitchen with quality appliances & an abundance of cupboard space.
Add to this ducted heating & evaporative cooling, 8x solar panels, tinted windows, large family-sized laundry & under-stair storeroom. Step outside to a wide backyard garden & peaceful surrounds, where your kids can play until their heart's content in complete privacy, it also boasts a fabulous decked & fully enclosable undercover entertaining area with clear PVC cafe blinds to satisfy the all seasons entertainer.
Walking distance to Hothlyn Drive buses, local shops, primary & secondary schools, local parks & Aitken Creek trails, it's close to childcare centres & kindergartens, Craigieburn Station as well as easy freeway access. A truly outstanding family lifestyle opportunity awaits the lucky family!
Insights: 3 Ilford Court, Craigieburn VIC 3064 was last sold in 2019 and 51 other 5 bedroom house in Craigieburn have recently been sold.

Description:
PERFECT LOCALE INCREDIBLY SPACIOUS
A contemporary designed home with a towering street presence, set in a tranquil street and surrounded by an abundance of beautiful parklands. For the kids, Aston Traffic Park, equipped with safety rules circuit for bikes/scooters at your doorstep, alongside Aitken Hill Primary School ideally located within walking distance and upcoming Craigieburn South Secondary School on Debonair Parade to be completed early 2020 as well as a future town centre around the corner on Vantage Boulevard.
This impressive 40sqs (approx..) home where the interior is flooded with natural light is the ideal lifestyle to raise a family, showcasing endless living areas where you cant help but be drawn to the grand open plan area with neutral colour tones, enhancing the stunning outlook of this residence.
The floor plan delivers 5 grand bedrooms, consisting of a spacious master with walk in robe plus additional his/hers double robes, extra-large shower to ensuite and private balcony retreat with beautiful sunset views overlooking the suburb.
Large walk-in- robes to 3 bedrooms upstairs and a desirable master-like bedroom downstairs with BIRs, alongside a bathroom fitted with large shower, perfect for guests or additional family members.
An executive study/office with an appealing French door entrance and fixed with suspended shelving.
A glamorous kitchen, showcasing a grand breakfast bar with attractive pendant lighting, is the centrepiece of the enormous living space with Caesar Stone benches, an enviable butler's pantry with power points, top shelf Omega 900mmcooktop and under bench oven, dishwasher and an abundance of cupboard space.
The open plan area is complemented with a reverse cycle spit system and recessed wall, perfect for a sizable, mounted television screen.
Youll love spending time in the upper level retreat area.
Flowing from the kitchen, step into a fully enclosed alfresco area, designed to allow year-round entertaining, with double sliding doors providing a seamless fusion between indoor-outdoor.
Comprehensive appointments include ducted heating, downlights, modern blinds, mirrored robes, substantial laundry with added storage room, convenient internal and rear garage access.
Outside delivers a low maintenance rectangular block of 460m2 approx. concreted all around plus both side accesses of the home.
Your local retail and food precinct is well catered for with 3km to Craigieburn Central and 4km to Highlands Shopping Centre with easy access to Aitken Blvd and Craigieburn Road.
Also, range of bus transport destinations available nearby.

Description:
Remarkable, Family Paradise
Built to exacting standards, this home is a class above. Having been built with style, expansive proportions throughout, and showcasing the finest of materials this masterpiece home is one not to be missed. Situated in Craigieburns finest pocket, within short distance to parklands, schools, transportation and Craigieburn central all nearby you will be suitably impressed.
The property itself is an entertainer's paradise - with a palatial entry and light filled foyer, secure entry from the garage leading into an inviting open plan kitchen all with the highest of quality fittings appliances with butlers pantry.
This luxury home includes a theatre room providing space for family time, as well as a large guest bedroom on the ground floor with BIR and a quality finished bathroom.
Upstairs you are greeted with a master fit for a king and queen inclusive of a balcony overlooking everything great Craigieburn has to offer. An impressive his and hers walk in robe and as expected enjoy the hotel style luxury ensuite with double vanity, 6 jet spa and an oversize double shower. The additional three bedrooms all have built in robes and enough space and privacy to accommodate the largest of families.
Further impressive inclusions include ; ducted heating, refrigerated cooling, high ceilings, double garage, side access, cctv camera, platation shutters throughout the whole ground floor and much much more
Come and inspect this charming property for yourself and be truly delighted.

Picture Perfect
Sure to make an impression that lasts, this beautiful family home is well situated within the Highlands Estate.
On offer are great sized bedrooms, master with ensuite and walk in robe, a well-appointed kitchen with SS appliances including 900mm cooktop, dishwasher PLUS walk in pantry, adjoining to the open plan meals and family area along with separate rumpus room, outside is a beautiful alfresco with plus decking gazebo.

Description:
Affordable Style & Unbeatable Convenience
In a blissfully quiet family-focused neighbourhood, this freestanding home is sure to leave a lasting impression with its generous design, immaculate presentation & central location to all of Craigieburn's facilities.
Beyond the gorgeous period-inspired facade, discover an impeccable interior comprising of 3 double bedrooms (master with walk-in his/hers robe & private ensuite), equally stylish main bathroom & separate WC, light-filled open living/dining area accompanied by a well-appointed kitchen with stainless steel cooking appliances.
Other stand out features include; high ceilings, ducted heating & powerful split-system air-conditioning, alarm system, full-size laundry plus lock up garage & low-maintenance front & rear yards.
Located to perfection within walking distance to local buses, Malcolm Creek trails & acres of parkland, close to primary & secondary schools, kindergarten/childcare, as well as easy access to shopping centres & the freeway.

Description:
SOMETHING SPECIAL IN A PRIME LOCATION
A lifestyle of complete luxury, comfort and space is assured to the occupant of this stunning home. Boasting a simple yet practical open floor plan, this well designed 29.8sq (approx.) home features a smooth integration between the stunning kitchen domain through to family meals area and decked alfresco entertaining space giving the home a free flowing feel. The gourmet kitchen features a massive 4 metre stone island bench, ample cupboard space, 900mm oven and impressive walk in pantry.
Sleeping quarters consists of large robed bedrooms master with huge dressing room and luxurious ensuite with double vanity. Additional bedrooms are well zoned and feature built in robes and are effortlessly complemented by the study area and sparkling centralised bathroom. To the rear of the home you will find a spacious theatre room which could be converted to a possible fourth bedroom or kids retreat.
Situated in a prime location and only walking distance Newbury Community Centre, Newbury Kindergarten, Newbury Primary School, Highlands Shopping Centre, Pelican Child Care, convenience stores, childrens parklands and much more.
Other features include: 900mm oven, ducted heating, 7 kilowatt split system, Hybrid flooring with built in underlay (25 year waterproof warranty), double blinds in bedrooms, drive through access, roller shutters, 5kws of solar, 2 and half car garage,
